====Pokémon Adventures====
{{main|Platinum (Adventures)}}
In [[Pokémon Adventures]], Dawn has a counterpart named Platinum. She is the daughter of the [[House of Berlitz]], the richest and most influential family in Sinnoh. After leaving home, she develops an interest in {{pkmn|battle|battling}} and goes on to challenge all of Sinnoh's [[Gym Leader]]s and the {{gdis|Battle Frontier|IV}}.
